---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/50 pt-10">
    <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8 text-lg">
        <Icon name="mdi:map-marker-question-outline" class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-500" />
        ¿Dónde puedo usar estos widgets?
    </h3>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-sm">
        <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col gap-3 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors group/item"
        >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                <Icon name="mdi:wordpress" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#21759b]" />
                WordPress
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                100% Compatible. Usa el enlace <strong>oEmbed</strong> (opción A) o el <strong
                    >iFrame</strong
                > (opción B).
            </p>
        </div>
        <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col gap-3 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors group/item"
        >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                <Icon name="mdi:web" class="w-5 h-5 text-black dark:text-white" />
                Wix / Shopify
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Busca el bloque "Incrustar sitio" o "HTML". Usa el enlace con <code
                    >?widget=true</code
                >.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col gap-3 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors group/item"
        >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                <Icon name="mdi:square" class="w-5 h-5 text-black dark:text-white" />
                Squarespace
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Añade un "Bloque de código" y pega el código <strong>iFrame</strong> completo.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col gap-3 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors group/item"
        >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                <Icon name="mdi:code-tags" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500" />
                Desarrollo a Medida
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Funciona en todas partes. Solo copia y pega el código <strong>iFrame</strong>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
